NeuAer,is,a,platform,that,allows,users,to,automate,actions,in,their,digital,lives,by,detecting,things,happening,and,things,around,users,in,their,physical,lives,Using,proximity,applications,NeuAer,allows,users,to,connect,their,phones,with,other,devices,and,items,The,NeuAer,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,NeuAer,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,connecting,devices,managing,devices,and,managing,account,information